reviews.text: Self service order n payment by octopus card good no queu
Kfc Tsim Tsa Tsui from meifoo station west rail station exit from N2 Tst station,, walk around 5 minutes to Kfc,, opposite side of Kowloon Mosque 🕌 near exit B2 Tst station
Everything was perfect. only thing was wrong is the manager himself, so rude and impolite. the food and anything else is much better than kfcs in my country
Something to try when in Asia, as they have their own local flavors.

It was my first time trying KFC In HK and I would say it’s very different! (In a good way) Very clean place and quick service ! My food was ready in about 3 minutes. The Chicken is delicious and fresh. Bathroom needs more cleaning however.

reviews.text: 有氣水喝有炸雞🍗👍🏻👍🏻😋😋

Dekat dgn hotel dan letaknya di pinggir jalan. Rasa standard KFC sehingga sama dgn rasa ayam KFC di Jakarta atau di Malang Jawa-Timur. Harga lebih Mahal stelah dikonversi ke rupiah. Bangku banyak tersedia, pelayanan pelanggan tidak ramah (khas muatan lokal) dan jangan smp lupa rute ke tempat penginapan ...

如果喜歡食炸嘢，香口嘅人，一定鍾意食，因為夠
野味，香脆，真的好味，
食咗都想下一次再嚟食🐔
食物而家炸食物炸得比以前好好多， 如果兩年之前我就唔夠膽推薦大家左呢間， 之前啲炸雞炸到過曬火。
Ada makanan ayam disini , cepat saji dekat masjid , siapkan kartu octopus mu
